Interface DependencyTreeNode

public interface DependencyTreeNode

The interface for a word in a dependency parse tree.

Method Summary

          Returns the index used by this DependencyTreeNode in an array.
 String lemma()
          The lemmatized version of the word, if there is any.

Method Detail

neighbors

List<DependencyRelation> neighbors()
Returns the list of neighbors to the current node. Note that this list include both relations where the current node is the head node and relations where the current node is the dependent.
